    "en": {
      "title": "Another ship is coming to Colombo tonight",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister Kanchana Wijesekara said on his official Twitter page that a ship carrying 100,000 metric tons of lubricating oil will arrive at Colombo port tonight.",
        "He also mentioned that another ship carrying 120,000 metric tons of lubricating oil will arrive in the country between 23rd and 29th.",
        "The minister further informed that these two oil tankers were sent from Russia. (R)"
      ],
